{pmatrix} a_{11} & a_{12}^T \\ a_{21} & A_{22} \\end{pmatrix}#Worked Example: $3 \\times 3$ Full Elimination":[96,123],"#$$ \\begin{pmatrix} 1 & 0 \\ -\\ell & I \\end{pmatrix} \\begin{pmatrix} a_{11} & a_{12}^T \\ a_{21} & A_{22} \\end{pmatrix}#Worked Example: $3 \\times 3$ Full Elimination#{1}":[98,123],"#$$ \\begin{pmatrix} 1 & 0 & 0 \\ 2 & 1 & 0 \\ 4 & 3 & 1 \\end{pmatrix} \\begin{pmatrix} 2 & 1 & 1 \\ 0 & 1 & 1 \\ 0 & 0 & 2 \\end{pmatrix}":[124,125],"#\\begin{pmatrix} 1 \\cdot 2 & 1 \\cdot 1 & 1 \\cdot 1 \\ 2 \\cdot 2 + 0 & 2 \\cdot 1 + 1 & 2 \\cdot 1 + 1 \\ 4 \\cdot 2 + 0 + 0 & 4 \\cdot 1 + 3 \\cdot 1 + 0 & 4 \\cdot 1 + 3 \\cdot 1 + 2 \\end{pmatrix}":[126,147],"#\\begin{pmatrix} 1 \\cdot 2 & 1 \\cdot 1 & 1 \\cdot 1 \\ 2 \\cdot 2 + 0 & 2 \\cdot 1 + 1 & 2 \\cdot 1 + 1 \\ 4 \\cdot 2 + 0 + 0 & 4 \\cdot 1 + 3 \\cdot 1 + 0 & 4 \\cdot 1 + 3 \\cdot 1 + 2 \\end{pmatrix}#{1}":[128,133],"#\\begin{pmatrix} 1 \\cdot 2 & 1 \\cdot 1 & 1 \\cdot 1 \\ 2 \\cdot 2 + 0 & 2 \\cdot 1 + 1 & 2 \\cdot 1 + 1 \\ 4 \\cdot 2 + 0 + 0 & 4 \\cdot 1 + 3 \\cdot 1 + 0 & 4 \\cdot 1 + 3 \\cdot 1 + 2 \\end{pmatrix}#Using $A = LU$ to Solve $Ax = b$":[134,147],"#\\begin{pmatrix} 1 \\cdot 2 & 1 \\cdot 1 & 1 \\cdot 1 \\ 2 \\cdot 2 + 0 & 2 \\cdot 1 + 1 & 2 \\cdot 1 + 1 \\ 4 \\cdot 2 + 0 + 0 & 4 \\cdot 1 + 3 \\cdot 1 + 0 & 4 \\cdot 1 + 3 \\cdot 1 + 2 \\end{pmatrix}#Using $A = LU$ to Solve $Ax = b$#{1}":[136,147],"#$$ \\begin{pmatrix} 1 & 0 & 0 \\ 2 & 1 & 0 \\ 4 & 3 & 1 \\end{pmatrix} \\begin{pmatrix} c_1 \\ c_2 \\ c_3 \\end{pmatrix}":[148,155],"#$$ \\begin{pmatrix} 1 & 0 & 0 \\ 2 & 1 & 0 \\ 4 & 3 & 1 \\end{pmatrix} \\begin{pmatrix} c_1 \\ c_2 \\ c_3 \\end{pmatrix}#{1}":[150,155],"#$$ \\begin{pmatrix} 2 & 1 & 1 \\ 0 & 1 & 1 \\ 0 & 0 & 2 \\end{pmatrix} \\begin{pmatrix} x_1 \\ x_2 \\ x_3 \\end{pmatrix}":[156,275],"#$$ \\begin{pmatrix} 2 & 1 & 1 \\ 0 & 1 & 1 \\ 0 & 0 & 2 \\end{pmatrix} \\begin{pmatrix} x_1 \\ x_2 \\ x_3 \\end{pmatrix}#{1}":[158,165],"#$$ \\begin{pmatrix} 2 & 1 & 1 \\ 0 & 1 & 1 \\ 0 & 0 & 2 \\